'''Xiaowen Delan''' (January 24, 2062 - March 27, 2156) was a Chinese businesswoman. 

==Early life and education==
Xiaowen was born in Lanzhou, one of the country's poorest regions. Her single mother was the model Fang Delan (2044 - 2126).

